{"tid":2449793,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"由恒生匯美金去sofi,  使唔使收手續費？","createTime":"2021-03-17T03:01:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T20:07:08.000Z","uid":295281,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2397fab4715254adab4f6a1942d957a0f89625fa","tid":2449793,"uid":295281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:01:26.000Z","msg":"本身諗住恒生可以直接係ebanking過美金去sofi匯豐美金戶口 , 點知恒生ebanking過美金只可以過番恒生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁焗我用匯款 過比sofi,  想問下如果咁樣過， 會唔會收手續費？<br />\n<br />\n我打比sofi,  佢話雖然係本地過本地， 但因為出過海， 可能要收35$美金 手續費<br />\n但我打上去恒生， 佢又話咁樣恒生呢邊唔使比手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下各位其實使唔使比手續費？<br />\n<br />\n同埋sofi話咁樣入金要5-7個工作天先到戶口<br />\non撚9 咁撚柒耐， 痴撚線， 我未開始用sofi買野， 開戶口已經搞9我一次， 入錢又搞9 我一次， 仲要咁撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我用支牛極快搞惦， 但我就係唔想用支牛先轉sofi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd5e4e26856715719c1969f43e30bf1006fafdc","tid":2449793,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:01:54.000Z","msg":"要"},{"pid":"fd2841ab7c441530a4567d1190ed6b4e9516ed6b","tid":2449793,"uid":295281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acd5e4e26856715719c1969f43e30bf1006fafdc","tid":2449793,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:01:54.000Z","msg":"要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:03:33.000Z","msg":"想問要收幾多？"},{"pid":"82f48e94331a7abf05af92309282c48598888892","tid":2449793,"uid":28378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:04:24.000Z","msg":"痕生唔收你commission in lieu of exchange？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884d2928f788459389cc490232bfba810406244e","tid":2449793,"uid":295281,"like":0,